entries.journal_entry_description: I need to make my way to Coronet, to meet with Frangee's boss, the CorSec Captain assigned to Coronet.
entries.journal_entry_title: Borvo's Guard - A Trip To Corellia
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: I've got Niksel Frangee's badge and I'm going to try to pass myself off as Niksel. He's been undercover so long all of his superiors have retired and been replaced. I should be able to pull this off. First I need to get to Corellia Capitol Building in Coronet.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: I need to try to bluff the CorSec Captain into believing I'm Niksel Frangee, the undercover agent who's been on Naboo for the last six years. The CorSec Captain's name is Thale Dustrunner and he's inside the Corellia capitol building.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: I'm going to have to take these meetings the Captain is sending me to in order to make sure they believe I'm who I say I am. When I'm done maybe I can find out why they're watching Borvo.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: I need to head back to Naboo and tell Borvo's Guard what I've learned. And also to drop off this stolen money.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: It's time to talk to Borvo's guard.
